			<div class="row">
				<div class="title">
					<div class="breadcrumbs"><div class="breadcrumb-node1" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb"><a href="/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="title">Home</span></a></div><div class="breadcrumb-node2" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb"><a href="/section/industry/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="title">INDUSTRY</span></a> </div><div class="breadcrumb-node3" itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb"><a href="/section/industry/companies/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="title">COMPANIES</span></a> </div></div>					<h1 itemprop="headline">Ahead of Reliance Jio, Bharti Airtel aims to be 4G&nbsp;whiz</h1>
					<h2 class="synopsis" itemprop="description">Bharti Airtel rolls out pan-India 4G service, offerings in a bid to stymie rival</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="leftpanel col-sm-8">

					<div class="dateline">
						<span>By: </span><a href="http://www.financialexpress.com/author/fe-bureau/" title="Posts by fe Bureau" class="url fn" rel="author">fe Bureau</a> |  
					New Delhi |  <span itemprop="dateModified" content="2015-08-07T01:33:16+05:30">
					August 7, 2015 1:33 AM					</span></div>
						<div class="leftpanel col-sm-8">
					<div class="utilitybox">
						<div class="social">
						    			          	<span class='st_fblike_hcount' displayText='Facebook Like' style="height:25px;"></span>
									
								<span class='st_facebook_hcount' displayText='Facebook'></span>
								<span class='st_twitter_hcount' displayText='Tweet'></span>
								<span class='st_googleplus_hcount' displayText='G+'></span>
								 								<span class='st_linkedin_hcount' displayText='LinkedIn'></span>
														</div>
							<div class="post-comment">
								<a class="comment-link" title="Comments" href="#vuukle_div" data-vuukle="115167"></a>
																 <a title="Print" class="print-link" id="print-link" href="http://www.financialexpress.com/article/industry/companies/ahead-of-reliance-jio-bharti-airtel-aims-to-be-4g-whiz/115167/99/print/" rel="nofollow"></a>															</div>
